Austin married his first wife, Kathryn Arnold, a dancer, in 1924 and divorced her in 1929.
He married wife number four, LouCeil Hudson, a singer, in 1949, and the marriage lasted until 1966.
Austin married Gigi Theodorea in 1967 — his fifth and final marriage.
